@Node "LOGLEVEL" "FFRS.guide/LOGLEVEL"
@Toc "General"

Setting your log level.
-----------------------

   @{b}*@{ub} Template : @{b}'LOGLEVEL <level>'@{ub}

     Valid loglevels range from 0 (no log writes) to 3 (for debugging
     purposes).  Defaults to 1, which will suit your needs in most
     cases.

     Example: LOGLEVEL 2

     Default: LOGLEVEL 1


@EndNode

@Node "File search" "FFRS.guide/File search"
