Initialize your node number.
----------------------------

   @{b}*@{ub} Template : @{b}'NODE <address>'@{ub}

     Your full FidoNet address (Zone:Net/Node.Point).

     This is also this address wich is used to get from the nodeliste
     your real name in a request file report.

     Example:  NODE 2:291/715.0


@EndNode

@Node "NODELISTPATH" "FFRS.guide/NODELISTPATH"
@Prev "NODE"
@Toc "Fidonet setup related parameters"

Setting up the nodelist path.
-----------------------------

   @{b}*@{ub} Template : @{b}'NODELISTPATH <path>'@{ub}

     Full path for nodelist access

     Example:  NODELISTPATH MAIL:Nodelist/

     Default:  No nodelist support


@EndNode

