Future versions.
****************

   @{b}*@{ub} Well, I am waiting for your suggestions, bug reports, comments,
     flames, large sums of money, etc. Especially, if you think FFRS
     should support the BBS program you run or have written, netmail me
     and I'll consider supporting your program.

     *item I am usually reading the international amiga sysops area (in
     FidoNet and AmigaNet) and the NETDEV_AMY (AmigaNet) wich replace
     the old FFRS_AMY (AmigaNet) conference.


@EndNode

