@Node "Registration ?" "FFRS.guide/Registration ?"
@Toc "Registration"

Registration ?
==============

   @{b}*@{ub} No more need to register FFRS, as explained just upper, so if you
     already have a keyfile, this one is also no more needed. May be, i
     you use FFRS, send me a netmail.

   @{b}*@{ub} I keep a mailing list of users so you'll be informed via netmail
     about future updates in case of other link problems.

   @{b}*@{ub} Don't forget to include your full (snail mail) address, any other
     information (what BBS you run, who you are, etc.) is appreciated.


@EndNode

